# Introduction 
HTC Riding is a ride-hailing simulation web app using OpenStreetMap for real-time routing. It calculates realistic fares with dynamic pricing based on distance, traffic, weather, peak hours, and vehicle type, and includes exclusive UEH student discounts to simulate real-world pricing variables
